# avisyslator_gnc usage

[日本語](README.md) | [English](README.en.md)

## Compiling

```shell
make
```

**After compiling, ``create_symbolmap_yaml.py`` will be exececuted and ``symbol_map.yaml`` will be automatically generated.*

## Setup (optional)

Edit `` test_case.yaml ``

## Running

```shell
./avsl test_case.yaml
```

## 出力確認方法

Graph `` time_seires_log_output.csv `` using `` plot.ipynb ``.
